---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Submissions">
    <main
        class="flex flex-col px-5 md:px-[3vh] lg:px-[12vh] xl:px-[32vh] space-y-10 my-8 font-medium"
    >
        <div>
            <h1
                class="text-3xl text-blue-800 my-4 ml-3 lg:ml-0"
                data-aos="fade-up"
            >
                SUBMISSION GUIDELINES
            </h1>
            <div
                class="pt-1 px-8 pb-9 bg-neutral-100 rounded-2xl"
                data-aos="fade-up"
            >
                <p class="text-2xl my-8 font-medium">
                    <ol class="text-lg">
                        <li>
                            1. Each author can submit only one paper; however,
                            they can be co-authors of multiple papers.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            2. Papers that canâ€™t be accommodated in the
                            technical sessions will be considered for poster
                            session. Authors need to indicate whether they would
                            want their papers to be considered for the poster
                            session at the time of submission.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            3. Submitted papers must be unpublished and original
                            work.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            4. Please submit a pdf version of the paper only.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            5. Please use the link to submit your paper. The
                            papers submitted through other channels will not be
                            considered.
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </p>
            </div>
